{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:13ReadiumShared8DOMRangeV","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DOMRange","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","title":"DOMRange","modules":[{"name":"ReadiumShared"}],"symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DOMRange","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/readiumshared\/domrange"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared"]]},"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/JSONEquatable","doc:\/\/Readium\/s28CustomDebugStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/Readium\/SQ"]}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Structures","anchor":"Structures","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/Point"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/init(json:warnings:)","doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/init(start:end:)"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/json"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/CustomDebugStringConvertible-Implementations","doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/Equatable-Implementations"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"This construct enables a serializable representation of a DOM Range.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DOMRange"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a DOM Range object, the startContainer + startOffset tuple represents the "},{"code":"start","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" boundary"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point. Similarly, the the endContainer + endOffset tuple represents the "},{"code":"end","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" boundary point."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In both cases, the start\/endContainer property is a pointer to either a DOM text node, or a DOM"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"element (this typically depends on the mechanism from which the DOM Range instance originates,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for example when obtaining the currently-selected document fragment using the "},{"code":"window.selection","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"API). In the case of a DOM text node, the start\/endOffset corresponds to a position within the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"character data. In the case of a DOM element node, the start\/endOffset corresponds to a position"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that designates a child text node."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"end"},{"type":"text","text":" field is optional. When only the start field is specified, the domRange object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"represents a “collapsed” range that has identical "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"start"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"end"},{"type":"text","text":" boundary points."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"https:\/\/github.com\/readium\/architecture\/blob\/master\/models\/locators\/extensions\/html.md#the-domrange-object","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://Readium/documentation/ReadiumShared/DOMRange/Equatable-Implementations":{"kind":"article","title":"Equatable Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/Equatable-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/readiumshared\/domrange\/equatable-implementations"},"doc://Readium/documentation/ReadiumShared/DOMRange":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DOMRange"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"DOMRange","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DOMRange"}],"url":"\/documentation\/readiumshared\/domrange","identifier":"doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"This construct enables a serializable representation of a DOM Range.","type":"text"}]},"doc://Readium/documentation/ReadiumShared/DOMRange/init(start:end:)":{"kind":"symbol","title":"init(start:end:)","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"start","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Point","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:13ReadiumShared8DOMRangeV5PointV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"end","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Point","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:13ReadiumShared8DOMRangeV5PointV"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Readium\/documentation\/ReadiumShared\/DOMRange\/init(start:end:)","url":"\/documentation\/readiumshared\/domrange\/init(start:end:)"},"doc://Readium/documentation/ReadiumShared/DOMRange/CustomDebugStringConvertible-Implementations":{"type":"topic","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/read